span><br><span class="line">target[count] = resourse[item];</span><br><span class="line">count++;</span><br><span class="line">item++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">flag = SearchReservedword(Reservedword, target);</span><br><span class="line">if (flag == -1)</span><br><span class="line">flag = 100;</span><br><span class="line">return;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">else if (IsNum(resourse[item]))</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">while (IsNum(resourse[item]))</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">target[count] = resourse[item];</span><br><span class="line">count++;</span><br><span class="line">item++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">flag = 90;</span><br><span class="line">return;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;无法识别\n&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">exit(0);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>该函数是整个程序的核心，对代码进行识别，通过改变flag的值来对单词进行分类，具体的分类是对应自己定义的编码表，因为程序中会存在双字符符号，例如+,++,+=之类的符号，所以要对+号的下一位进行判断才能确定该符号为什么符号，这样的话在判断后就要直接返回该符号具体的编码，而不是通过查询符号表数组来解决（注意：最后要考虑字符无法识别的情况，像出现标识符以数字开头的情况，这样就违背了标识符的定义，属于无法识别的字符）</p><ul><li>主函数<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">int main()</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">char resourse[10000] = &#123;&quot;&quot;&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">char target[20] = &#123; &quot;&quot; &#125;;</span><br><span class="line">int i = 0;//记录数组长度</span><br><span class="line">int flag = -1;//0：程序结束符号，1~32：保留字，33~74：符号，90：常数，100：标识符</span><br><span class="line">FILE *f1, *f2;</span><br><span class="line">if ((f1 = fopen(&quot;F:\\test\\test.cpp&quot;, &quot;r&quot;))==NULL)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;读取文件test失败\n&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">exit(0);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">if ((f2 = fopen(&quot;F:\\test\\text2.txt&quot;, &quot;w+&quot;)) == NULL)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">printf(&quot;读取文件text2失败\n&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">exit(0);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">while (true)//读取f1中的内容</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if (feof(f1))</span><br><span class="line">break;</span><br><span class="line">resourse[i] = fgetc(f1);</span><br><span class="line">i++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fclose(f1);</span><br><span class="line">cout &lt;&lt; resourse &lt;&lt; endl;</span><br><span class="line">resourse[i] = &apos;\0&apos;;</span><br><span class="line">Clearnotes(resourse, i);</span><br><span class="line">i = 0;</span><br><span class="line">while (flag != 0)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">LexicalAnalysis(resourse, flag, target, i);</span><br><span class="line">if (flag == 100)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">for (int j = 0; j &lt; 100; j++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">if (strcmp(Identifier[j], target)==0)//标识符已经在表中</span><br><span class="line">break;</span><br><span class="line">else if (strcmp(Identifier[j], &quot;&quot;) == 0)//未写入，将标识符写入表中</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">strcpy(Identifier[j], target);</span><br><span class="line">break;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fprintf(f2, &quot;（标识符，%s）\n&quot;, target);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">else if (flag &gt;= 1 &amp;&amp; flag &lt;= 32)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">fprintf(f2, &quot;（保留字：%s)\n&quot;, Reservedword[flag - 1]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">else if(flag==99)</span><br><span class="line">fprintf(f2, &quot;（常数，%s）\n&quot;, target);</span><br><span class="line">else if (flag &gt;= 33 &amp;&amp; flag &lt;= 74)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">fprintf(f2, &quot;（符号，%s）\n&quot;, Operator[flag - 33]);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fclose(f2);</span><br><span class="line">return 0;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>主函数的主要作用是接收识别函数的返回值，并将其二元组形式输入到指定文件中。</p><h3 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h3><ul><li>编码表为自己所定义，本程序的编码表不够完全，可根据需要自行添加，但要一一对应，并且最好是不要轻易更改。</li><li>对于每一个函数最好是有相应的测试代码进行测试，这样会大大减小代码出错的可能性和减轻最后代码错误查找的工作量。</li><li>由于代码很长，很容易出现一些代码编写的错误，例如某一个’==’写成’=’号之类的，并且程序中存在很多变量，要非常注意这些变量的改变是否符合逻辑。  </li></ul><p>[参考博客：]<br>[1]:<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/zyrblog/p/6885922.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.cnblogs.com/zyrblog/p/6885922.html</a></p><p>[GitHub仓库链接：]<br>[1]:<a href="https://github.com/nikedown/Lexical-analyzer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/nikedown/Lexical-analyzer</a></p>]]></content>
    
